      "rationale": "Before architecture work, refactors, dependency tracing, or 'where is this implemented?' tasks: check graphify-out/GRAPH_REPORT.md, use it to identify relevant modules/files, and only fall back to broad search when the report is missing, stale, or insufficient.",
