      "source_location": "## MemPalace Usage",
      "source_url": null,
      "captured_at": null,
      "author": null,
      "contributor": null,
      "rationale": "Use MemPalace when the user says something was discussed before, prior architecture decisions matter, the task depends on earlier reasoning, or previous plans/conventions must be recalled. Do not use for every task; verify recalled memory against the repo.",
